  "description": {
    "zh": "所以，我感觉你回来收集一些武器数据了，对吗？猜你是在找工作，你找到我真是太好了，我的哥们，我有工作要完成。我知道我可以依靠你的技能 here，而且你知道我付钱很大方，对吧捍卫者？\n\n总之，我们来说说你实际的任务……突击卡宾枪。\n没错，你没听错，兄弟。\n\n能搞定吗？用市场上能买到的这些武器各干掉一些目标。我估计这要花你一些时间，但我希望很快能听到你的消息！祝你好运，捍卫者。",
    "en": "So, I have the feeling that you came back to collect some data on weaponry, am I right? Guessing that you're looking for work, good thing you reached out to me my guy, I got work to be done. I know I can rely on your skills here, and you know that I pay well, right champion?\n\nAnyway let's move on to your actual task... Assault Carbines.\nIndeed, you heard that right brother.\n\nGonna take care of it? Take out some targets with each of these weapons that are available on the market. I assume this will take you some time, but I expect to hear from you very soon! Good luck out there champion."
  },
